<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nitum ngeilohna gamah,
 Khawpi hawihtak a um;
 Beimang kit ngei ta puona,
 Zie chun &quot;Zan a um puoi.&quot;

[V2]
 Lalpa'n mitthi thiekhul ding,
 Thih leh nat lauhna beita;
 Kum kisimna um ta puo'n a,
 Ziechun &quot;Zan a um puoi.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Akawt suongmantam a siem,
 Zie khawpi hawih achun;
 Khawlai sana tui luon,
 Ziechun &quot;Zan a um puoi.&quot;

[V4]
 3. A kawt kikhak ta puo'n a,
 Zie khawpi hawih tak chuh;
 Hinna lui a luongzing hi,
 Ziechun &quot;Zan a um puoi.&quot;

[V5]
 4. Nisa vak a ngai ta puoi,
 Zie khawpi hawih achun;
 Belam No chuh vak ahi,
 Zie chun &quot;Zan a um puoi.&quot;</lyrics>
<title>NO NIGHT THERE</title>
<hymn_number>381</hymn_number>
</song>